3. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper deals with multiple access control in communication networks, which falls under the domain of networking and internet architecture. 
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper uses concepts from control theory to study the dynamics of the game. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with multiple access control in a communication channel, which can involve multimedia data.
